01:20:34.451 --> 01:20:37.738
What, if... if I live my dream,
you'll live yours?

01:20:37.818 --> 01:20:39.504
Yeah.

01:20:39.668 --> 01:20:41.518
Want to swear?

01:20:42.751 --> 01:20:46.237
- Sure, motherfucker.
- No, I mean it.

01:20:46.317 --> 01:20:48.052
Let's do this.

01:20:48.518 --> 01:20:52.119
If you go back on this, I will come at
you in the black of some terrible night.

01:20:52.199 --> 01:20:55.268
And I will bring a pointy reckoning
that will shudder you.

01:21:04.384 --> 01:21:06.585
I'm through with breaking promises.

01:21:40.918 --> 01:21:43.237
- Don't fall.
- Too late.

01:21:43.317 --> 01:21:46.151
- Shut up.
- Okay.

01:22:13.184 --> 01:22:14.752
Jonah!

01:22:28.968 --> 01:22:30.171
Rex?

01:22:39.918 --> 01:22:42.318
Rex! Hey.

01:25:16.836 --> 01:25:23.841
<i>Oh, now feel it coming back again</i>

01:25:28.923 --> 01:25:35.597
<i>Like a rolling thunder chasing the wind</i>

01:25:40.673 --> 01:25:47.138
<i>Forces pulling from the center
of the Earth again</i>

01:25:52.314 --> 01:25:56.112
<i>I can feel it</i>

01:25:58.177 --> 01:26:01.866
<i>I can feel it</i>

01:26:04.028 --> 01:26:08.077
<i>I can feel it</i>

01:26:09.685 --> 01:26:12.538
- Come on.
- <i>I can feel it</i>

01:26:12.618 --> 01:26:14.258
Let's get out of here.

01:26:18.451 --> 01:26:19.951
Jonah.

01:26:46.217 --> 01:26:48.618
Jonah! Stop!

01:26:57.717 --> 01:27:00.551
What was that place? Who is that man?

01:27:00.917 --> 01:27:04.285
- I don't know him.
- He looked familiar.

01:27:05.017 --> 01:27:08.837
We meet him twice.
First time, you don't remember.

01:27:08.917 --> 01:27:11.185
The second time, you never forget.

01:27:38.317 --> 01:27:40.384
What if I lied to you?

01:27:41.050 --> 01:27:43.018
When I said I didn't want to grow up?

01:27:52.551 --> 01:27:54.104
Run.

01:27:54.184 --> 01:27:56.870
Run! Run!

01:28:13.817 --> 01:28:15.395
Jonah!

01:28:45.151 --> 01:28:46.851
We need more light.

01:29:00.917 --> 01:29:02.485
Hey.

01:29:04.317 --> 01:29:06.318
They can't hurt us if we stick together.

01:29:07.217 --> 01:29:09.305
They won't let us go forward.

01:29:09.784 --> 01:29:13.251
Then let's go back,
where the dreams are true.

01:29:14.017 --> 01:29:15.637
The stories too.

01:29:51.284 --> 01:29:54.351
Jonah. Jonah.

01:31:08.717 --> 01:31:10.584
We need to go higher.

01:32:05.184 --> 01:32:07.051
My best friend.

01:32:07.717 --> 01:32:10.151
Why did we leave all this behind?

01:32:10.784 --> 01:32:13.584
- We needed more.
- Did you?

01:32:15.550 --> 01:32:17.721
<i>Do you remember that day?</i>

01:32:18.051 --> 01:32:20.055
<i>Like it was yesterday.</i>

01:32:20.135 --> 01:32:23.302
<i>It kinda was, since we kept it so close.</i>

01:32:25.617 --> 01:32:27.704
<i>It was Halloween then too.</i>

01:32:28.084 --> 01:32:31.704
<i>We were all dressed up.
I still had my first camera.</i>

01:32:31.784 --> 01:32:33.784
<i>Don't make it too real.</i>

01:32:34.684 --> 01:32:39.837
<i>It was getting late. And it isn't midnight
when young boys turn into pumpkins.</i>

01:32:39.917 --> 01:32:42.550
<i>It's when the street lights turn on.</i>

01:32:44.784 --> 01:32:46.617
<i>It was a bad idea.</i>

01:32:47.617 --> 01:32:51.051
<i>The boys knew that from the start, but...</i>

01:32:52.151 --> 01:32:54.751
<i>...nobody wants to be the one left behind.</i>

01:32:58.650 --> 01:33:02.051
<i>Even though tunnels
can be longer than they appear.</i>

01:33:05.184 --> 01:33:09.665
<i>And there are things in this world
we don't read about in storybooks.</i>

01:33:15.984 --> 01:33:19.871
<i>Wolves may lurk in any guise.</i>

01:33:20.984 --> 01:33:23.018
<i>And only in the dark...</i>

01:33:23.450 --> 01:33:26.684
<i>...do we learn how far we'll go to survive.</i>

01:33:27.817 --> 01:33:30.851
<i>Even if it means running
as fast as you can...</i>

01:33:31.717 --> 01:33:34.564
<i>...and leaving behind everything you value.</i>

01:33:42.317 --> 01:33:43.818
Corey.

01:33:48.784 --> 01:33:51.817
<i>And that was the last time
that they played Cocytus.</i>

01:34:14.117 --> 01:34:16.184
It'll be morning soon.

01:35:05.316 --> 01:35:07.185
Is it getting cold?

01:35:08.884 --> 01:35:10.751
