01:35:16.950 --> 01:35:18.951
We have to go home eventually.

01:35:21.283 --> 01:35:23.284
Then the game will be over.

01:35:28.617 --> 01:35:31.061
What would happen if we change the ending?

01:35:33.250 --> 01:35:34.851
What ending?

01:35:36.850 --> 01:35:38.851
To the story in the drain.

01:35:41.750 --> 01:35:43.617
What if I...

01:35:50.884 --> 01:35:53.433
- ...what if he stayed?
- He left.

01:35:56.316 --> 01:35:58.184
Maybe he didn't.

01:36:02.784 --> 01:36:04.984
Maybe it just seemed like he did.

01:36:07.450 --> 01:36:10.517
And as he was walking away, he turned back...

01:36:11.050 --> 01:36:13.651
...'cause he realized
who his real friend was.

01:36:14.384 --> 01:36:18.144
'Cause together, they could do anything.
They could cross the bridge to Cocytus.

01:36:18.223 --> 01:36:21.650
They could outwit the darklings.
They could outrun the wolves.

01:36:22.051 --> 01:36:24.450
Why couldn't they defeat two bullies?

01:36:25.750 --> 01:36:27.604
And then?

01:36:27.684 --> 01:36:30.884
