01:37:12.216 --> 01:37:14.284
Yeah, real mature, smart-arse.

01:37:16.917 --> 01:37:19.150
Thought you were in a hurry to grow up.

01:37:22.283 --> 01:37:24.517
Maybe I was a bit hasty on that one.

01:37:25.750 --> 01:37:27.617
Good to hear it.

01:37:45.850 --> 01:37:47.650
I'm sorry.

01:37:51.617 --> 01:37:53.417
For leaving.

01:37:57.550 --> 01:37:59.416
You know...

01:37:59.683 --> 01:38:01.150
...tonight...

01:38:02.617 --> 01:38:04.884
...kind of made up for the rest of it.

01:38:18.917 --> 01:38:20.750
Turn around.

01:38:33.917 --> 01:38:35.550
Jonah!

01:38:36.116 --> 01:38:37.984
Hey, Jonah!

01:38:54.817 --> 01:38:58.050
Oh, fuck! Fuck! Jonah!

